**Plague Pit** | Plague Team Group
__Basics__
The Plague Pit group contains all members of the Plague team.
__Members__
<?PlagueBearer:> Plague Bearer
<?PlagueCarrier:> Plague Carrier

__Formalized__
Unique Group
Starting: Display `Rodents` (Counter)
On Disbandment: Remove `Contaminated` from @All [Condition: not (@(Align:Plague) exists)]
